# 🔧 MEMBER A — Prototype Developer Roadmap

## What You're Building: FairLens

A **web-based AI Bias Detection & Mitigation Dashboard** that:
1. Accepts a CSV dataset and a trained model (or generates synthetic data)
2. Computes fairness metrics across protected attributes (gender, race, age, etc.)
3. Flags discriminatory patterns with visual heatmaps and charts
4. Uses **Gemini API** to generate plain-English bias audit reports and fix suggestions
5. Applies debiasing techniques and shows before/after comparison
6. Runs on **Google Cloud Run** (satisfies Google Cloud deployment requirement)

