## Key Bias Metrics to Implement

| Metric | What it measures | Fair threshold |
|---|---|---|
| Demographic Parity Difference | Δ in positive prediction rate | ≤ 0.1 |
| Disparate Impact Ratio | Ratio of selection rates | ≥ 0.8 (80% rule) |
| Equalized Odds Difference | Δ in true/false positive rates | ≤ 0.1 |
| Statistical Parity Difference | Difference in P(Ŷ=1) between groups | ≤ 0.05 |
| Average Odds Difference | Average of FPR and TPR difference | ≤ 0.1 |

